8 An Act relating to motor vehicles; requiring certain
vehicles be registered as a motor vehicle; stating
9 certain license endorsement not required; requiring
driver be of certain age; amending 47 O.S. 2021,
10 Section 11-805.1, which relates to low-speed electric
vehicles; requiring certain vehicles be in compliance
11 with certain national standards; requiring vehicle
identification number for certain operation;
12 authorizing Service Oklahoma to register and license
certain vehicles; authorizing Service Oklahoma to
13 promulgate certain rules; and providing an effective
date.
